<div container="container-fluid">
  <div class="index-background"></div>
  <div id="text-overlay">
    <h2>Dogs make the best company.</h2>
    <p>However, the alarming fact is that approximately 3.9 million dogs are abandoned each year.* Our mission is to
      educate and better connect humans with dogs in the effort to decrease this number. Allow us to help you discover
      the breed that fits your lifestyle, or help us help others by creating a profile for your dog. </p>
    <button class="main-button"><a href="/usersurvey">Get Matched</a></button>
    <button class="main-button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#join">Create a Dog Profile</button>
    <p class="source">*Source: <a href="https://www.dosomething.org/facts/11-facts-about-animal-homelessness" target="_blank">DoSomething.org</a></p>
